<!-- Node: "Call of Duty: United Offensive" -->
<div class="body_box_header">Call of Duty: United Offensive</div>
<div class="body_box"><small>Submitted by <a href="http://www.gamedesign.net/user/view/1804" title="View user profile.">Kingpin_Xatrix</a> on Thursday, March 25, 2004 - 21:23</small><br /><br />
New game by <a href = "http://www.gmistudios.com/">Gray Matter</a> (RTCW, Kingpin, etc.) revealed!!<br>
Their new game is an expansion pack for CoD, <b>Call of Duty: United Offensive</b>. It will include 3 Single Player campaigns. You can also play as US, Russian or British side.
United Offensive scheduled to release this fall.
